 for"],[296,367,"how they treat you."],[367,558,"It's fine, I can handle a couple of"],[558,667,"rich bitches."],[817,963,"Okay, I'm going to help you"],[963,1017,"find this watch."],[1017,1117,"And once I do, you have to promise"],[1117,1317,"to help me save my mom, okay?"],[1376,1618,"I'll keep my word."],[1618,1856,"But if we don't find that watch,"],[1856,2022,"you're good as dead."],[2022,2173,"What is that? What was."],[2173,2310,"Did you just threaten me?"],[2310,2398,"It's not a threat."],[2398,2660,"It's the truth."],[2660,2790,"Well,"],[2790,3040,"I'm trying to help you, okay?"],[3040,3132,"Killing me,"],[3132,3211,"if I don't find a the watch,"],[3211,3432,"that's a little bit of an overreaction."],[3666,3745,"Don't misunderstand me."],[3745,3937,"Okay?"],[3937,4045,"I don't want you to die."],[4112,4412,"Then what is your problem?"],[4483,4696,"There are people after me."],[4696,4846,"And if I don't stay ahead of them,"],[4846,4975,"they won't just kill me."],[5080,5380,"They'll kill anyone who helped me."],[5463,5576,"That means if we don't find that"],[5576,5726,"watch,"],[5726,5834,"we both die."]],"44":[[533,713,"Okay, it's not in the storage closet."],[713,880,"So, it literally has to be here"],[880,1009,"somewhere."],[1084,1288,"Well, it better be."],[1288,1551,"Our lives depend on it."],[1551,1589,"I'm sorry."],[1589,1751,"Can you explain to me"],[1751,1976,"how a watch is worth killing over?"],[1976,2206,"Because I just don't understand."],[2206,2410,"It's an heirloom passed down to"],[2410,2602,"each mafia boss as the previous one"],[2602,2748,"passes."],[2773,3073,"So why does my mom have it?"],[3474,3649,"She's holding onto it for my father."],[3649,3791,"Okay, well, the cops won't let"],[3791,3858,"her take any calls,"],[3858,3937,"so we're gonna have to wait"],[3937,4062,"till she's out and -"],[4062,4154,"My father is dying."],[4291,4487,"He has to pass on the watch before -"],[4542,4675,"Oh my God, Jax."],[4675,4904,"I'm so sorry."],[4904,5117,"I didn't know."],[5180,5372,"I'm really sorry."],[5372,5530,"Without the watch, his successor can't"],[5530,5751,"prove he was chosen."],[5751,5943,"That means war as every son of a bitch"],[5943,6076,"tries to take over."],[6076,6106,"Okay,"],[6106,6243,"So who's he going to choose?"],[6656,6815,"You?"],[7044,7211,"What you don't think I can do it?"],[7211,7403,"No. I mean,"],[7403,7570,"that's not what I'm saying."],[7570,7711,"I think they would be lucky to have"],[7711,7870,"you lead them."],[8683,8971,"Every don needs a powerful woman."],[8971,9188,"Me? No, no, I am, I'm way too young."],[9188,9342,"I'm still in high school."],[9342,9530,"And I would be too."],[9530,9726,"If I didn't ditch it for the family business."],[9868,10168,"So then you are way too young."],[10322,10623,"Wait."],[10723,10977,"Look at this."],[11019,11156,"Tiffany's family was going to buy"],[11156,11319,"this place?"],[11486,11786,"Looks like the offer was rejected."],[11891,12016,"Oh my God."],[12016,12170,"Oh my God. That's. That's why."],[12170,12303,"That's why Tiffany made Micah frame"],[12303,12366,"my mom!"],[12483,12612,"To sell this place out!"]],"45":[[183,312,"This is it. This is it."],[312,496,"This is the proof we need."],[496,533,"We can."],[533,709,"We can free my mom."],[934,1184,"This isn't enough proof."],[1184,1309,"They set up your mom, the St. Clairs"],[1309,1438,"are powerful."],[1568,1780,"To take them down we need more."],[1780,2081,"Well, what else do we need to do?"],[2185,2339,"Let's find the watch."],[2339,2506,"Once I'm the successor, I'll bring"],[2506,2652,"the full force of the mafia down"],[2652,2694,"on them."],[2781,2890,"We've been searching for, like,"],[2890,3044,"an hour Jax!"],[3044,3215,"I don't know where this watch is."],[3215,3365,"I know."],[3853,3953,"Where's a white rabbit"],[3953,4154,"when you need one?"],[4166,4300,"But Zoey in Wonderland"],[4300,4491,"can still find the missing watch."],[4550,4771,"Once she lets Jax make a move"],[4771,4850,"on her."],[4896,5196,"After all, this is life or death,"],[5238,5492,"and we all know he's been dying to"],[5492,5555,"kiss her."],[5818,5976,"I have to kiss Jax"],[5976,6277,"to find the watch and save our lives?"],[6343,6506,"Well, gossip godmother"],[6506,6719,"hasn't been wrong yet."],[6719,6827,"What's got you all shaken up?"],[6827,6915,"What?"],[6915,7002,"Me? No, nothing."],[7002,7144,"I don't know what you're talking about."],[7144,7215,"Let me see that."],[7215,7340,"Hey, Jax!"],[7340,7407,"Just stop it!"],[7407,7524,"What is it, Finn? Checking up on"],[7524,7565,"you?"],[7565,7703,"No, no, it's not that...."],[8470,8591,"It's my turn with you."],[8683,8858,"I want to kiss him."],[9017,9167,"But I can't fall for someone so"],[9167,9317,"dangerous."],[9509,9701,"I knew it."],[9701,9780,"You want this too."]],"46":[[479,642,"Even if Gossip Godmother hadn't"],[642,817,"told me to kiss him."],[850,992,"I'd want to."],[1109,1334,"I've come this far."],[1334,1426,"You go the rest of the way."],[1426,1580,"If you want me back."],[3086,3244,"What?"],[3244,3386,"Almost done boss?"],[3411,3445,"Yeah."],[3445,3570,"Almost."],[3995,4083,"Wait a second."],[4083,4154,"Hold on."],[4558,4733,"That was way too light."],[5084,5184,"No way."],[5184,5372,"The watch!"],[5372,5467,"You found it!"],[5876,6177,"Well, I kept my end of the promise."],[6197,6402,"Now, you have to do the same."],[6402,6564,"Help me save my mom now!"],[6564,6723,"I will."],[6723,7023,"I'll do anything for you."],[7077,7173,"All right, let's give this to my dad."],[7173,7198,"Come on."],[8641,8700,"Finn!"],[8954,9017,"What are...."],[9075,9255,"What are you doing here?"]],"47":[[70,154,"What?"],[246,408,"What are you doing here?"],[408,629,"I got concerned, so I came to check"],[629,704,"on you."],[725,850,"I'm good."],[850,1146,"We found what we were looking for."],[1146,1309,"Oh, excellent, then you don't need Zoey"],[1309,1355,"anymore."],[1368,1455,"Actually I was just -"],[1455,1530,"Boss,"],[1530,1718,"it's for you."],[1718,1805,"Code red."],[2544,2656,"I need to take care of this."],[2831,2973,"I'll find you later."],[3603,3732,"All set with the jealous act?"],[3732,3858,"Or should I get popcorn?"],[3858,4083,"Zoey, I'm not jealous, I just -"],[4233,4404,"Did he, did he hurt you, or?"],[4404,4625,"What? No he didn't hurt me."],[4733,4788,"We..."],[4842,4975,"I was helping him find"],[4975,5105,"his dad's watch."],[5105,5217,"And he's going to help me save my"],[5217,5305,"mom now."],[5305,5568,"Zoey, you can not forget, he is mafia!"],[5568,5714,"You can not trust him!"],[5851,6031,"He may be mafia, but."],[6031,6151,"He's been way more honest with"],[6151,6368,"me, then any of the so called elite"],[6368,6560,"families like the St. Clairs."],[6869,6944,"Did..."],[6944,7073,"Did he...."],[7073,7303,"Did he kiss you?"],[7511,7728,"So you are jealous."],[7728,8058,"Yes, yes I am."],[8108,8316,"What are you going to do about it?"]],"48":[[29,141,"Nothing."],[229,371,"Your feelings are your problem."],[371,538,"I would like to make them your problem."],[946,1059,"That was my stomach."],[1059,1272,"He didn't feed you?"],[1272,1393,"Well then let's get you sorted with"],[1393,1580,"some food, yeah?!"],[1780,1935,"So...."],[1935,2135,"Pancakes for dinner?"],[2135,2323,"It's the only thing I know how to make."],[2352,2477,"I love it."],[2777,2932,"You know, I do not think your mom is"],[2932,3078,"going to like that I'm here right now."],[3094,3244,"She's going to freak out."],[3244,3403,"Oh once she gets to know you, she'll"],[3403,3499,"love you."],[3636,3820,"I doubt that..."],[3820,3874,"Okay!"],[3874,3995,"After we eat, we need to go"],[4074,4225,"Go pick up my mom, okay?"],[4408,4487,"Don't worry about it."],[4487,4675,"It's already taken care of."],[4838,5017,"What, what do you mean?"],[5017,5188,"Zoey, your mom is on her way to my"],[5188,5276,"house, right now."],[5472,5605,"Are you serious?"],[5605,5668,"Yeah."],[5918,6031,"Finn, thank you!"],[6031,6210,"Thank you, thank you."],[6210,6264,"You don't know what"],[6264,6335,"this means to me."],[6414,6527,"You're welcome. And that mafia"],[6527,6881,"prince can back off now, you don't"],[6881,7032,"need him anymore."],[7207,7403,"Already in the arms of another man."],[7403,7524,"Jax!"],[7524,7699,"What are you doing here?"]],"49":[[0,158,"Already in the arms of another man."],[158,246,"Jax!"],[246,442,"What are you doing here?"],[746,846,"The watch, you're wearing the watch,"],[846,900,"does that mean?"],[900,1051,"Dad made me heir."],[1051,1146,"I'm running things now."],[1380,1605,"Congratulations, I'm so proud of you."],[1643,1805,"Jax that's amazing."],[1976,2089,"I'm so happy for you."],[2089,2160,"Thank you."],[2293,2373,"So, um..."],[2423,2577,"You've crashed our meal to flex your"],[2577,2669,"new title?"],[2781,2965,"I made Zoey a promise."],[2965,3082,"And I intend to keep it."],[3082,3269,"It's okay actually, my mom's on her"],[3269,3424,"way here right now."],[3424,3666,"But she still needs to go to trial."],[3858,4070,"Okay, well..."],[4070,4187,"We still need to expose the St."],[4187,4308,"Clairs for framing her."],[4375,4471,"They're powerful though."],[4471,4562,"I'm going to need some actual"],[4562,4721,"evidence."],[4813,4921,"Aren't you in the mafia?"],[5063,5271,"Can't you just, like, fix it?"],[5630,5714,"Murder is messy,"],[5764,5826,"okay?"],[5955,6097,"Plus, it's much more satisfying to"],[6097,6222,"watch them burn."],[6364,6598,"And, they do have a weak link."],[6652,6769,"Tifffany."],[6815,6936,"I hate her."],[7023,7082,"I do!"],[7282,7411,"But..."],[7545,7686,"That's a good idea..."],[7778,7853,"Okay."],[7920,7999,"Okay."],[8053,8191,"If I can push the right buttons, I can"],[8191,8266,"get her to confess."],[8558,8621,"Right?"],[8646,8796,"I just need the right moment."],[8796,8938,"And..."],[8938,9075,"Prom is this weekend."],[9075,9292,"Go, get her to confess, on record."],[9292,9505,"Once she breaks, I'll tear down her"],[9505,9626,"whole family."],[10573,10723,"Jax!"],[10723,10923,"You need to calm down, okay?"],[10923,11061,"I'll text you, we'll meet up later."],[11119,11182,"Do you really want to"],[11182,11482,"stay with these posh pricks?"],[11786,11874,"Stay with me instead."]],"50":[[183,358,"Zoey's not going anywhere."],[492,575,"How about you let her speak for"],[575,613,"herself?"],[613,684,"Thank you!"],[684,792,"That's a great idea."],[829,1042,"Finn, I don't want to stay with you,"],[1042,1176,"because your mom hates me."],[1280,1593,"And your dad is sick."],[1618,1826,"You have a lot on your hands."],[1826,2052,"I don't want to bother you. Okay?"],[2052,2110,"Zoey."],[2110,2223,"My mom is all bark, you,"],[2223,2352,"just ignore her."],[2352,2477,"My dad wants to thank you"],[2477,2706,"personally for finding his watch."],[3015,3186,"Stay or go."],[3186,3378,"Does it even matter?"],[3378,3616,"Either way, you end up at prom."],[3616,3891,"So follow your heart or your"],[3891,4024,"other instincts."],[4137,4379,"Jax is dangerous."],[4379,4521,"Exciting."],[4521,4821,"He makes me feel unstoppable."],[4821,4859,"Finn's"],[4859,5267,"steady, safe and really cares"],[5267,5359,"about me."],[5609,5910,"I'm going to stay here tonight."],[6160,6435,"You win this time."],[6435,6581,"But I always get what I want."],[6715,6931,"And I want Zoey."],[8504,8587,"The next time"],[8587,8708,"that you have to see him. I'm"],[8708,8850,"coming with you."],[8850,9150,"I will not have my girlfriend alone"],[9200,9296,"with a criminal."],[9296,9426,"I'm not your girlfriend, we're just"],[9426,9547,"pretending to date, Finn."],[9755,9943,"Zoey, I'm..."],[10147,10389,"I'm a royal billionaire."],[10472,10664,"I could have chosen literally anyone"],[10664,10865,"if I needed a fake girlfriend."],[10902,11019,"And,"],[11265,11398,"I didn't,"],[11398,11544,"I chose you."],[11945,12116,"But it was all fake..."],[12162,12462,"No, it wasn't."],[12479,12612,"Not for, not for me."]],"51":[[137,221,"This is insane."],[221,291,"It is."],[291,425,"Can you believe they actually live her?"],[425,696,"No, look, I don't..."],[838,980,"I missed you so much!"],[1080,1217,"I missed you so much, I'm so glad"],[1217,1343,"that you're here."],[1343,1447,"Oh, don't worry."],[1447,1559,"It'll be okay."],[1559,1647,"I know."],[1672,1793,"And look!"],[1793,2093,"Jax had this delivered."],[2097,2248,"Open it."],[2248,2352,"Okay."],[2585,2761,"Oh my God."],[2777,2919,"Oh my God."],[3107,3232,"There's a note."],[3374,3536,"It's hard to find a gown that's as"],[3536,3628,"special as you are."],[3628,3812,"but this one comes close."],[4300,4496,"Zoey..."],[4496,4742,"This is a vintage Marinelli."],[4742,4896,"Tens of thousands of dollars."],[4896,5030,"Mom, this is way too nice."],[5030,5113,"I can't wear this."],[5113,5330,"Nonsense."],[5388,5526,"You show those snobs that you don't"],[5526,5689,"need money to get the Prince."],[5718,6018,"Royal or Mafia."],[6060,6135,"Try it on."],[6135,6181,"Okay."],[7344,7469,"I told you to meet us there."],[7528,7640,"Yeah, and I didn't listen."],[7640,7716,"I noticed."],[7782,7903,"Just go eat some beans, alright?"],[7970,8095,"Would you stop it."]],"52":[[29,350,"Hey, baby girl, you're gorgeous!"],[1514,1639,"Ok."],[1639,1906,"I need you two, to stop the alpha act,"],[1906,2031,"for just tonight."],[2114,2156,"Okay?"],[2156,2335,"Look at me! Focus!"],[2389,2515,"We have one goal."],[2515,2702,"And that is to make Tiffany confess."],[2748,2923,"So what's the plan?"],[3015,3257,"We need to provoke her somehow."],[3432,3620,"I need another post from the future"],[3620,3920,"to tell me how to take Tiffany down."],[3928,4045,"Prom night."],[4045,4245,"Zoey's not here to dance."],[4245,4425,"She wants revenge."],[4425,4617,"Her target, the scheming"],[4617,4808,"heiress who set her mom up."],[4867,4992,"Weapon?"],[4992,5292,"Taking that prom queen crown."],[5559,5855,"I'm running for prom queen."],[6410,6619,"When I win prom queen, I'll let each"],[66